reviews.text:
A nice station but could do with a a good clean, especially with the Tour de Yorkshire finishing here on Thursday. Plants are dead, stairs and platforms need jet washing. Not a very good welcome to visitors.

Well done, thank you for the cleaner station.

I have had a couple of problems with trains to and from Selby. Without me asking for more to be done the customer service manager, B Field, went above and beyond to assist me - unknowing that I started my day to Selby with a cancelled train. Wow, such service is not something one experience these days.
Some of the best things to get from here and being a charity shop others benif from the sales too
Staff friendly and helpful station very tidy cafe good lots of timetables and information available
Excellent car buying place trueman quality cars selby. I am very please with the car and services provided. Thanks
